    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You focus on the elemental energies of the target or on the equipment they are wearing, and leach it away from them. When you Cast this spell, select one of the Priming elements available to you. This focus spell gains the trait that matches the primed elements you use in its casting. The creature must make a Fortitude saving throw.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Critical Success </strong>Your target is unaffected.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Success </strong>Your target’s resistance to the chosen element is reduced by half your level.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Failure </strong>Your target’s resistance to the chosen element is reduced by your level. If it is reduced to 0 or is not resistant to it, any carry over amount is turned into weakness equaling that amount instead.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Critical Failure </strong>As failure, but if the target’s resistance is reduced to 0, it gains weakness to that element equal to your level instead.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Special: </span>If you are wielding a primed weapon, you can add a material component to the spell and add this element ontop of the one you have selected, allowing you to affect 2 elements at a time. This spell gains the primed weapon’s elemental trait.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Heightened (4</strong></span><sup><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">th</strong></span></sup><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">) </strong>You can target 2 creatures in range.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Heightened</strong> <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">(8</strong></span><sup><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">th</strong></span></sup><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">) </strong>Creatures who fail or critically fail lose damage immunities to your chosen elements.</span></p>"
